UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The power of Elune compels you!  The power of Elune compels you!  \n\nGo now!  Seek out Jandria in the central hall of the Temple of the Moon in the southern section of Darnassus!', `FemaleText`='The power of Elune compels you!  The power of Elune compels you!  \n\nGo now!  Seek out Jandria in the central hall of the Temple of the Moon in the southern section of Darnassus!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=5346; -- 5346
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The dishes that Alegorn whips up are to die for.  He''s always busy preparing new delicacies over in the Craftsman''s Terrace.  Be sure to try his Cenarion Green recipe if he has any left.  \n\nNow, if you don''t mind, I must investigate this rash of missing deer. ', `FemaleText`='The dishes that Alegorn whips up are to die for.  He''s always busy preparing new delicacies over in the Craftsman''s Terrace.  Be sure to try his Cenarion Green recipe if he has any left.  \n\nNow, if you don''t mind, I must investigate this rash of missing deer. ', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=5358; -- 5358
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn''t spill a drop, but now I can''t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  \n\nYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He''ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.', `FemaleText`='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn''t spill a drop, but now I can''t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  \n\nYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He''ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=5365; -- 5365
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf''s corpse.  It''s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  \n\nNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties.', `FemaleText`='We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf''s corpse.  It''s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  \n\nNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=5373; -- 5373
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='"A skill for those who wish to overcome obstacles."  I believe that is how Faelyssa describes her skill set.  \n\nIf you believe as she does then find your way to the Cenarion Enclave in the northern section of Darnassus where she conducts her class.', `FemaleText`='"A skill for those who wish to overcome obstacles."  I believe that is how Faelyssa describes her skill set. \n\nIf you believe as she does then find your way to the Cenarion Enclave in the northern section of Darnassus where she conducts her class.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=5375; -- 5375
