UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Hello. By odd twist of fortune, we have obtained the remains of Kel''Thuzad''s feared abomination Patchwerk.  Our researchers are able to reassemble them in various ways to test the mettle of your band of would-be heroes, should you so desire.  \n\nWe can construct a sturdy Patchwerk against which to measure your ability to do damage, a brutal Patchwerk who will deliver rapid and mighty blows to any who would dare stand before him, or a well-rounded Patchwerk who will test your entire fighting force.\n\nWhich would you prefer?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=35872; -- 35872
