UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The Earthwatchers won''t allow faction squabbling to jeopardize the Earthen Ring''s work here.\n\nThose who break the peace will be dealt with... harshly.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=41698; -- 41698
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The Wildhammers have always embraced shamanism, aye, but to find ourselves beneath the sea as part of the Earthen Ring?\n\nIt would''ve taken more than a few tankards for me to believe that one, a year ago.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=41700; -- 41700
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='In my youth, my family did not approve of my interest in shamanism. Brash and foolish as I was, I ran away from them and practiced on my own.  Upon returning to my home one day, I found my parents gone. My home destroyed. They never found who did it.\n\nI''ve spent my life striving to extend my shamanistic visions to see into the past - to find out what happened to my family and who is responsible. I''ve come a great way. I''ve learned to focus in on impactful events in the recent past, but I have much further to go if I ever hope to glimpse something that occurred so long ago.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=42495; -- 42495
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Blackrock Caverns, a level 79-81 dungeon on Blackrock Mountain, is now available for testing. Please be in your full group before teleporting to the dungeon. Meeting Stones are not available for this dungeon yet.\n\nTo leave the Halls of Stone, simply exit through the normal exit inside the dungeon and you will be teleported to Dalaran. If you die and release, you should teleport back from this NPC.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=42825; -- 42825
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Throne of the Tides, a level 79-81 dungeon in Vashj''ir, is now available for initial testing. The dungeon is very much a work in progress, and the final boss is not available. Please be in your full group before teleporting to the dungeon. Meeting Stones are not available for this dungeon yet.\n\nTo leave the Throne of the Tides, simply exit through the normal exit inside the dungeon and you will be teleported to Dalaran. If you die and release, you should teleport back from this NPC.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=43476; -- 43476
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The excitement of the crowd, the thrill of the fight - you should have seen it!  Ever since those ogres took control of the Dire Maul arena, I''ve been forced to camp out here.  Griniblix the Spectator - ha!  Spectator of what?  This campfire?  That shrub?  Or how about this odd purple tree?\n\nListen, if you''re looking for a fight, Skarr was headed towards the Lariss Pavilion, and The Razza was soaring in the direction of the New Thalanaar.  Just be sure to let me in on the betting before the bloodbath begins!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=43556; -- 43556
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Bossy, I need to ask something great of you.  I need to cut off your head to prove my loyalty to the Bloodsail Buccaneers, so they will allow me to infiltrate their ranks and hopefully discover their true intentions.\n\nBooty Bay needs you, Bossy... now more than ever.\n\n', `FemaleText`='Bossy, I need to ask something great of you.  I need to cut off your head to prove my loyalty to the Bloodsail Buccaneers, so they will allow me to infiltrate their ranks and hopefully discover their true intentions.\n\nBooty Bay needs you, Bossy... now more than ever.\n\n', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=43570; -- 43570
