UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='I see you''ve arrived. \n$bThis is the eve of the sundering, when the collapse of the Well of Eternity fractured the continents of the world.\n$bHere, we will snatch up the Dragon Soul before it is lost to the mists of time.\n$bBut first, you must bring down the protective wards of Azshara''s lackeys. You will find them within the palace. I will scout on ahead.\n$bGood luck, heroes!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=54122; -- 54122
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Sloppy, but adequate.  You seem capable in a fight and in need of direction.\n$bThere are hundreds of demons ahead, it would be suicide to go it alone:', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=54220; -- 54220
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The shadows will hide us well.\n$bI am concealed by this shadowcloak, and can imbue its magics onto you.\n$bIt will not make us invisible, but as long as we keep our distance from our foes we will remain hidden.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=54224; -- 54224
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Anything outside of that circle around you will not be able to see you, but the illusion will fade if you attack or take damage.\n$bI suggest you remain hidden until I say otherwise, these demons are too powerful to face head on and in full force.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=54226; -- 54226
