UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Out for the day at Halfhill Market.\n\n- Ella', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=57549; -- 57549
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Betrayed! We came here every week. They seemed to be simple traders. \n\nNow these... fish-men greet us with one webbed hand, all the while with the other behind their back, holding their knives, waiting for us to turn around so they can plunge them in!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=58538; -- 58538
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Hey, kid! You all right?\n\nI''ve got you. Don''t go into the light!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=58605; -- 58605
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Gone to Halfhill Market. Don''t touch my vegetables!\n\n- Farmer Fung', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=58637; -- 58637
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='<Threaten him with violence.>\nA debt is a debt. Let''s see the money.', `FemaleText`='<Threaten him with violence.>\nA debt is a debt. Let''s see the money.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=58776; -- 58776
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='<Offer to pay off his debt.>\nDon''t worry, Jambeezi. I will pay your share today.', `FemaleText`='<Offer to pay off his debt.>\nDon''t worry, Jambeezi. I will pay your share today.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=58778; -- 58778
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The first group that came - the Trolls... they cared nothing for us - walked right past us, pushing our families out of the way.\n\nThe next, though - the mercenaries. They took us prisoner, stole from our homes, and threatened us with death if we resisted.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=60207; -- 60207
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='My people, corrupted...\n\nShai Hu, a local warrior, was the first to drink of the tainted waters.\n\nHe was strengthed, emboldened, and urged the others to do the same.\n\nI warned them against it. I sensed danger, corruption...', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=60937; -- 60937
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Well you can''t just stay in here! You leave me no choice!\n<Use the Fire Lotus Incense.>', `FemaleText`='Well you can''t just stay in here! You leave me no choice!\n<Use the Fire Lotus Incense.>', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61102; -- 61102
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='We are discussing where we shall go next. Perhaps join the Pearlfin in Jade Forest?\n\nSpeaking of which - how does the $ngill Tribe sound to you?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61142; -- 61142
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='How does fortune smile on me so? My son, my livelihood returned to me... \n\nTo have thought that one day I was simply content with all this. How truly lucky I was!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61145; -- 61145
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='I can''t believe how I felt before.\n\nTo think that I could have become posessed by the same thing that controlled these Jinyu, it''s... disturbing, to say the least.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61148; -- 61148
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='As Waterspeaker, I performed many rituals. There is one, though, that I have never performed - to purify mental corruption.\n\nIt is an ancient ritual, one which we have not needed since days of legend, when Shaohao walked Pandaria.\n\nI fear we need it now...', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61162; -- 61162
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='While I would love to purify all of my corrupted bretheren, I cannot allow those of us who have not fallen to corruption to go leaderless.\n\nWe must stop the spread of this vile influence, and then I will lead those of us who remain pure to freedom.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61167; -- 61167
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Every Shado-Pan makes three eternal oaths:\n\nTo defend this land, to protect its people, and to train their pupil.\n\nWhen a Shado-Pan dies, they must be released from these bonds.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61493; -- 61493
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Ah, it was a difficult battle. So sad to have lost friends.\n\nThough, I am glad I had them build the battlefield refreshment device.\n\nWithout it, and without the power of my stout brew, who knows how many more would have been lost...', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61494; -- 61494
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='We could use a $c. Glad to see my husband sent you along.\n\nI''m a scout, not much for face-to-face combat. And Lao-chen here... well, normally he''s a fighter, but he''s still exhausted from the last battle.\n\nAnd, he''s too busy cooking up some scheme.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61501; -- 61501
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Lin is upset - Zhiya was his good friend and we lost him in the battle. \n\nI don''t want Lin to do something thoughtless. I don''t know what I''d do if I lost him...', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61657; -- 61657
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Zhiyao dead. Shiya dead. Liu dead.\n\nSuna councils me to calm, but honor demands otherwise.\n\nTaran Zhu sits safe in the monastery while we defend the pass alone? Why shut us out? Why not send reinforcements?\n\nThese questions trouble me.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61658; -- 61658
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='At first, my deference and respect for Taran Zhu prohibited me from questioning his decision to close the monastery to outsiders.\n\nThen, when the yaungol first attacked, my focus on the battle at hand prevented me from leaving the front lines to question his inability to send reinforcements.\n\nNow, three Shado-Pan lie dead, one is captured, and my patience is beyond worn thin - it is gone. I plan to go to the monastery and demand an audience with Taran Zhu.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61674; -- 61674
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Well, you really sent them flying. I could hear their... bleating from here. \n\nBleating? Is that what you call the sound of a yaungol flying off a wall?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61691; -- 61691
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Wow. I could hear the explosions from up on the wall.\n\nI guess not ALL of Lao-Chen''s ideas are terrible.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61692; -- 61692
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Another attack?!\n\nThese yaungol will not relent until we push them back into Townlong. Or, even better, into the sea.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61696; -- 61696
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='After all this... our brothers and sisters passing, Lin captured by yaungol, my beer gone, I think it''s time to move along.\n\nPerhaps I''ll take the fight to the mantid...', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61700; -- 61700
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='This city is so unlike anything from home...\n\nAh, friend, how may I help you?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61809; -- 61809
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='These are my kind of people. Sure, maybe Garrosh is a bit intense, but you can really feel like they''re going somewhere!\n\nAnyways, what can I show you about being a monk, friend?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=61825; -- 61825
