UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The essence font allows you to break down weapons and armor into enchanting materials.  The item is PERMANENTLY destroyed.\n\nDo you wish to continue?', `FemaleText`='The essence font allows you to break down weapons and armor into enchanting materials.  The item is PERMANENTLY destroyed.\n\nDo you wish to continue?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=82176; -- 82176
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='I''ll move forward and scout their gates while you''re taking out those catapults. Lok''tar ogar!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=82486; -- 82486
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='We need to spread news of our victory. Take the fey dragon and meet me back at Embaari Village.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=82762; -- 82762
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='I''m well aware that the fish are more plentiful in the upper pools. However, a real professional knows that the big ones prefer a spot with a little more cover. \n\nJust wait until Roluna sees what I can land down here in the weeds!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83103; -- 83103
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='A trader with an empty cart, such a sad sight, no? \n\nIf only my partner Daruun would make up his mind so we could be on our way.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83118; -- 83118
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='It''s a lovely plant, yes? What color would be best suited for Shattrath''s markets? \n\nDoes anyone even buy plants these days?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83119; -- 83119
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Together, we have crushed the slavers and brought upon them swift destruction. They who have taken everything from me. \n\nBut, I have one last thing to give. To be a part of something greater... I''d forgotten what that feels like.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83167; -- 83167
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='In my profession I have learned that the nature of crystals is very much like that of the Draenei people. \n\nThe core material has amazing potential, but begins as rough and heavily flawed. It is only through careful shaping and nurturing that its potential can truly be reached. \n\nOnly then can it show its magnificent beauty and wondrous clarity.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83192; -- 83192
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Oh, that? I may have hitched a ride through your garrison portal. \n\nThey should probably guard those things better, come to think of it.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83336; -- 83336
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='The skies hold untold wonders, waiting to be discovered. Our researchers study the stars and beyond over at the observatory. \n\nIf you have time, traveler, I would recommend paying it a visit.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83346; -- 83346
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='The ranchers of Embaari raise elekk and talbuk to supply Shattrath, as well as many of the smaller draenei villages. \n\nIf you wish to review the livestock, you can find their ranches along the outskirts of the village.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83347; -- 83347
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='<Laanda lowers his voice to a whisper.>$B$BYou have the appearance of an ally, but I cannot speak long. I am working to infiltrate the ranks of the Sargerei, to take down their system from within. So far, no one suspects my identity.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83552; -- 83552
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Eww, some of these supplies are really water logged and... sticky? These will get the job done, but truly, this is disgusting.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83671; -- 83671
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='What little supplies we had upon arrival are quickly being used up for the needs of the refugees. \n\nI hope we are able to leave here soon, lest we become stranded in Auchindoun just like them.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83691; -- 83691
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Take care, the demons can strike again at any moment. It seems the Shadow Council will stop at nothing to breach the gates of Auchindoun.\n\nWe must remain vigilant!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83728; -- 83728
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Some of the larger demons can tear through our ballistae relatively quickly. \n\nIf I can''t produce them more rapidly than they get destroyed, then there may be no stopping the Shadow Council.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83763; -- 83763
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='I understand that our relationship with the Draenei has been through some trying times, but right now, these soldiers need my help. \n\nWe need to stick together if we all wish to defeat the Shadow Council.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83776; -- 83776
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='These pilgrims gather from all over Draenor to hear the wisdom of the spirits interred at Auchindoun. \n\nFor the draenei people, such wisdom comes with great reward.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83796; -- 83796
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The skirmishes with the Shadow Council have left many travelers stranded in Auchindoun. \n\nUnless the tide of battle turns, it is likely we will never leave this place.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83797; -- 83797
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='These great defense crystals are just one of the myriad uses for the crystals in the Jorune mine. \n\nIt is a pity that the Shadow Council forces us to use them only for instruments of war.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83804; -- 83804
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Tressia was a good solider, but when the venom took its hold on her, she left me no choice. \n\nI hope we wipe every member of the Shadow Council from the face of Draenor. Our people deserve better than to end up like this.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83823; -- 83823
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='<Lets out a soft, deep groan>', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83825; -- 83825
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='So far, none of our medicines have had any effect on the spiders'' poison. \n\nWe must gather more specimens before we can concoct an effective antidote.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=83870; -- 83870
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='In order to successfully train a fey dragon, one must keep them well fed and rested. A restless dragon tends to be less than receptive to orders.\n\nPlease do not disturb them.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=84047; -- 84047
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Here is where we train the young fey darters to follow commands. \n\nThough their antics may seem silly, the discipline they learn now is imperative if we ever wish them to take a rider.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=84049; -- 84049
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Brighteye is one of the smartest fey dragons we''ve trained at the Draakorium. He loves doing tricks for visitors!\n\nWhy don''t you see if Brighteye can do a trick for you?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=84064; -- 84064
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='Start the garrison invasion?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=84130; -- 84130
