UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Prove allegiance to your guild by conquering all the dungeons in Draenor with your guild mates.  Once you complete this task, you may purchase Garrison Guild Banners from the Guild Vendor.\n\nCome see me once you have acquired the item and I will help you display guild banners in your Garrison for all to see.', `FemaleText`='Prove allegiance to your guild by conquering all the dungeons in Draenor with your guild mates.  Once you complete this task, you may purchase Garrison Guild Banners from the Guild Vendor.\n\nCome see me once you have acquired the item and I will help you display guild banners in your Garrison for all to see.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87483; -- 87483
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='You have never heard of Nat Pagle? The man is a legend!\n\nNat has traveled the world over, always looking for the biggest catch! Speaking of big catches, I bet there are some huge catches for us out here in Draenor. If only we could get Nat to come out here and teach us the way...  Keep working on that fishing skill and come back to me when you are fully trained.', `FemaleText`='You have never heard of Nat Pagle? The man is a legend!\n\nNat has traveled the world over, always looking for the biggest catch! Speaking of big catches, I bet there are some huge catches for us out here in Draenor. If only we could get Nat to come out here and teach us the way...  Keep working on that fishing skill and come back to me when you are fully trained.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87538; -- 87538
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='What can you tell me about this "Nat Pagle" character?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87540; -- 87540
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Once I get this thing working we''ll be able to clear-cut this island in no time flat.\n\nLasers, baby!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87559; -- 87559
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Whoa! You are here too? Phew... I was starting to think I made a bad call. I''m ready to win this war for the Alliance, $GSir:Madam;!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87636; -- 87636
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Come one, come all. Witness fights to the death in the one and only Ring of Blood! Today we have $n and $Ghis:her; pals foolishly going up against Skull Chewer! Time for some more skulls, buddy!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87650; -- 87650
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Dead $Gman:woman; walking, folks. $n and $Ghis:her; allies are entering the world famous Ring of Blood to test themselves versus Rotvine, living weapon of destruction! This will be a slaughter to see!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87660; -- 87660
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='$n and $Ghis:her; allies want to prove their worth against Mogor''s prize beast: Dreshax, the Corpse Mauler! This worm has consumed the bones of countless fallen hopefuls - can $n come out of this alive?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87661; -- 87661
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Much thanks again, mon, for gettin'' me back my gear. \n\nNow da fishes don''t stand a chance against Abu''gar!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=87855; -- 87855
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='You seem surprised to see us here, $C. It is understandable. I am all too familiar with how the arakkoa have treated your people.\n\nThe Adherents of Rukhmar are savage creatures, and their lust for power can only lead to their downfall. We seek a different path.\n\nWe search for artifacts of the Apexis so that we may use them to initiate a peaceful new beginning for the arakkoa. In exchange for these relics, we offer finely crafted goods, which we hope you will find equal in value.\n\nWould you see it fit to aid us, $C?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88041; -- 88041
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='I greet you, $C. We are the Order of the Awakened, and we represent the best interests of the arakkoa people.\n\nI am certain that you have witnessed the horrors brought upon the arakkoa and others by the Adherents of Rukhmar. We wish to reverse this damage and bring about a peaceful new era for our society. To do this, however, we require the knowledge of the Apexis.\n\nIf you wish to assist us, we will trade valuable items for any Apexis relics you happen upon. What say you, $C?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88048; -- 88048
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Miss Chi-Yuan possesses a talent in inscription which I can only hope to one day achieve.\n\nIf you wish to be trained on the subject, there is no finer instructor than she.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88125; -- 88125
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The local draenei have been indispensable allies in our fight here in Ashran. \n\nSo long as we keep a steady stream of supplies from the mainland, our victory is assured!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88158; -- 88158
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='People always wonder how a Worgen becomes a stablehand, but the truth is, I''ve been doing this long before I got afflicted. Just leave your pets with ol'' Orville and I''ll take good care of them.\n\nAnd before you ask, yes, I promise I won''t eat them.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88160; -- 88160
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `Type`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88166; -- 88166
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Thanks again for doin'' me a service back dere in Nagrand, mon. Eva'' since da Lich King be forcin'' me into his service, all I eva'' want ta do is get away an'' do some fishin''.\n\nDis Draenor place be much nicer dan Northrend for fishin'', ya know. Ya don''t have ta worry about da ice, and da fish be a lot less likely ta eat ya.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88521; -- 88521
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Enter the portal when you are ready to teleport.  You will be sent directly to Stormshield on the island of Ashran.\n\nHave no fear, Stormshield will not flag you for PVP.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88530; -- 88530
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Enter the portal when you are ready to teleport.  You will be sent directly to Warspear on the island of Ashran.\n\nHave no fear, Warspear will not flag you for PVP.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88531; -- 88531
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Murg used to be a peon just like these orcs, but I got to be the best stone cracker out there!\n\nNow, they give Murg the name "Stonecrack" and lets me boss around these little guys. It''s the best job, I tell ya!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88630; -- 88630
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='This Murg guy is great. It''s a real inspiration watching him yell at those peons.\n\nMaybe after we get off this rock, I''ll acquire his services for some of my operations.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=88632; -- 88632
