UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Da Alliance think dey so smart. Dey hidin'' behind dis truce of deirs, meanwhile dey searchin'' dis island high and low for a powerful weapon, but dey no askin'' for our help.\n\nSure, dey say da weapon is ta be used against da Iron Horde, but what is ta stop dem from turnin'' it on us once we off dis world?\n\nI say we take da weapon, and we be showin'' dem who has da powah - on dis world as well as ours.\n\nFor da Horde!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90535; -- 90535
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='I''m sorry $Gladdie:lass;, but I can''t give you access to the vault.\n\nThis is where Dr Jones is keepin'' his artifacts secure. Even though the Explorer''s League is allowing adventurers to store their gear in the extra space, the vault stays off limits.', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90706; -- 90706
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Zarg like kitties. Zarg train his little kitties to be cute little warriors. \n\nWhat? Why you look at me like that? \n\nYou got something against kitties?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90794; -- 90794
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='You need talk to Varzok in Orgrimmar!  Any guard there should be able to give directions to him.\n\nDa portal to Orgrimmar inside shaman hut.  Good luck!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90795; -- 90795
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='After the toll taken from our assault on the Dark Portal, much of our remaining forces came to regroup here in Ashran. It is unfortunate that hostilities with the Alliance came shortly after.\n\nDo you seek refuge here, as well, or do you wish to stoke the flames of battle further?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90810; -- 90810
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `FemaleText`='These trolls aren''t so bad. They may be skinny and talk funny, but they make a fun spear launcha! \n\nI can''t wait to skewer some dwarves with this thing!', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90812; -- 90812
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='The sign reads:\n\n"I''m Commander $n, and this is my favorite merchant in Warspear."', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90814; -- 90814
UPDATE `broadcast_text` SET `MaleText`='Not now! These humans have brought in all of this mouth watering meat! Just look at it! Imagine, gnashing and shredding it with your fangs. The juices and the ripping of meat from the bone as you''re devouring it... \n\n<The worgen''s eyes wander off...>\n\nWhat did you want again?', `VerifiedBuild`=19831 WHERE `ID`=90930; -- 90930
